ARTICLE 5 ( 3 ) OF REGULATION ( EEC ) NO 2194/85 IS HEREBY AMENDED AS FOLLOWS :
1 . IN THE FIRST SUBPARAGRAPH, "FOR THE 1985/86, 1986/87 AND 1987/88 MARKETING YEARS' IS REPLACED BY "UNTIL 31 DECEMBER 1992';
2 . IN THE THIRD SUBPARAGRAPH, "FROM THE 1988/89 MARKETING YEAR ONWARDS' IS REPLACED BY "FROM 1 JANUARY 1993 ONWARDS '.
